parameters.description:
Stringified JSON object with a subset of properties of the expected object.
                               Selects all objects that exactly match the specified properties.
                               Note: take care to URL encode your parameter.

    {
        "lastName": string,
        "externalId": string,
        "emailAddress": string,
        "postalAddress": {
            "city": string,
            "country": string,
            "postalCode": string
        }
    }
